OL,3,CTravel disruption as Tube drivers
OL,4,Cstage second strike of the week
OL,6,FLondon Underground drivers staged
OL,7,Ftheir second strike of the week on
OL,8,FThursday causing fresh disruption for
OL,9,Ftravellers in the capital.
OL,11,FThe Circle and Waterloo & City lines
OL,12,Fare not running at all on Thursday.
OL,14,FThere are part suspendions on the
OL,15,FCircle Line between Liverpool Street
OL,16,Fand White City; on the Metropolitan
OL,17,FLine between Baker Street and Aldgate,
OL,18,Fand on the Picadilly Line between
OL,19,FArnos Grove and Uxbridge, as well as
OL,20,FHeathrow Terminals 4 & 5.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
