OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780578664
OL,3,CTravel disruption as Tube drivers
OL,4,Cstage second strike of the week
OL,6,FThere are severe delays across the
OL,7,Fentire district and northern lines.
OL,9,FMembers of the Rail, Maritime and
OL,10,FTransport union (RMT) also walked out
OL,11,Fon Tuesday after last-ditch talks
OL,12,Ffailed to resolve a dispute over a
OL,13,Ffour-day week.
OL,15,FThe two sides met for five hours on
OL,16,FMonday, with the assistance of the
OL,17,Fconciliation service Acas, but the
OL,18,Ftalks ended without any resolution.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
