CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780578664
OL,3,CTravel disruption as Tube drivers
OL,4,Cstage second strike of the week
OL,6,FPicket lines were again mounted
OL,7,Foutside Tube stations on Thursday and
OL,8,Fbuses were busier than usual.
OL,10,FTube lines were suspended or disrupted
OL,11,Fbecause of the strike, which the union
OL,12,Fsaid was being solidly supported.
OL,14,FThe RMT added that talks were expected
OL,15,Fto resume next week.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
