OL,3,CTravel disruption as Tube drivers
OL,4,Cstage second strike of the week
OL,6,FTransport for London said Londoners
OL,7,Fand visitors to the city were still
OL,8,Fable to travel despite the strike
OL,9,Faction on Tuesday adding that more
OL,10,Fthan 60% of drivers came to work
OL,11,Facross the day.
OL,13,F"We continue to urge the RMT to work
OL,14,Fwith us to resolve their questions on
OL,15,Fthe proposed four-day week and to
OL,16,Fsuspend any future action while that
OL,17,Fwork is completed," said a
OL,18,Fspokesperson.
