OL,3,CTravel disruption as Tube drivers
OL,4,Cstage second strike of the week
OL,6,F"The data highlights the continued
OL,7,Fimpact transport disruption can have
OL,8,Fon central London, with many people
OL,9,Fonce again changing their usual
OL,10,Froutines and journeys."
